@startuml
title Strategy - intercambio en runtime
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class ImageEditor <<Context>>
  interface FilterStrategy <<Strategy>>
  class GrayscaleFilter
  class ContrastFilter

}

FilterStrategy <|.. GrayscaleFilter
FilterStrategy <|.. ContrastFilter
ImageEditor --> FilterStrategy : delega algoritmo
Main ..> ImageEditor : usa contexto


note bottom of ImageEditor
La estrategia puede cambiar sin modificar el contexto.
end note
@enduml
